Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.51,Penguin_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,总裁大人
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.99,Penguin_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,わしより強くなれ　マリオ
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,要比我更强 万里夫
